{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"bb206dcf-6e25-4255-a2f2-ec7093285291","content":"No workflow files found in the current directory, so here's general guidance for the switch:\n\n### Changes needed for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. NuGet.org setup**\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a new trusted publisher, linking your GitHub repo, branch/tag filter, and workflow file path\n\n**2. Workflow changes**\n\nAdd `id-token: write` permission and replace the `dotnet nuget push` API key with `--source` pointing to the OIDC endpoint:\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token\n      contents: read\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      # Build & pack steps...\n\n      - name: Install .NET\n        uses: actions/setup-dotnet@v4\n\n      - name: Publish to NuGet (trusted publishing)\n        run: dotnet nuget push \"**/*.nupkg\" --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**3. Key differences**\n\n| Before (API key) | After (OIDC) |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` in push command | No secret needed |\n| `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` | Remove `--api-key` entirely |\n| No special permissions | `permissions: id-token: write` |\n\n**4. Remove the old secret**\nOnce verified, delete `NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo's **Settings → Secrets**.\n\nThe `dotnet nuget push` command (with .NET SDK 8.0.4+) automatically requests an OIDC token from GitHub Actions and authenticates with NuGet when no API key is provided and `id-token: write` is set.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"e7551c97-0d7f-402d-9d56-68031dc484c9","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"No workflow files found in the repository. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to trusted publishing (OIDC). Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":510,"requestId":"1424:3CD672:127BAE8:14C9E52:6A027ABB"},"id":"28aa2a21-da4b-4b87-a637-e08cc07f162a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T00:56:38.633Z","parentId":"dc2973ee-a4c3-4015-9dcf-d41250449f86"}
